In 2024, kids still listen to this 30 years old lady "Obak Bhalobasa". A chain bond for 2 or 3 generations. I won't talk about the quality of the composition. This is pure emotion for us, a 90's kid, became kid again, for seven long minutes. 
Love Warfaze, 
Love Arnob

snippet.textDisplay: "Obak Bhalobasha" by Warfaze is a timeless masterpiece that transcends genres. Its melancholic beauty and powerful emotions resonate with listeners on a deep level. The song's contrasting elements, from the soft vocals to the driving rock instrumentals, perfectly capture the complexities of love. It's a testament to Warfaze's (Babna Bhai) songwriting prowess and a landmark song in Bangla music. What a remake, Salut.

snippet.textDisplay:
One of the highest level of compositions in Bangla Music industry. Obaak Bhalobasha is a timeless song. You can put this masterpiece in any generational phase and it would amaze, entertain everyone like it always did.
40 years of Warfaze, yet more to go, man! A band aged 40, but feels like it's still the youngest. No doubt why it's the best band in Bangladesh and one of the toppest in the whole Asia. Warfaze forever!🤍
